##Puppet 
1. Puppet is a software configuration management tool which includes its own declarative language to describe system configuration. 
It is a model-driven solution that requires limited programming knowledge to use. Puppet is produced by Puppet Inc.  
It is founded by Luke Kanies in 2005.

